331
00:21:47,119 --> 00:21:48,480
[SPEAKER_00] Logično, ne kupe istog trenutaka.

332
00:21:48,559 --> 00:21:50,799
[SPEAKER_00] Sad sam ja stavila, na primjer, kolica 2000 eura.

333
00:21:51,599 --> 00:21:55,200
[SPEAKER_00] Nije sad deset ljudi odmah ošli i kliknuli i kupili kolica 2000 eura.

334
00:21:55,279 --> 00:21:58,400
[SPEAKER_00] Ali su ljudi vidjeli ta kolica i kad će im trebati, to oni.

335
00:21:58,799 --> 00:22:00,400
