347
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,920
[SPEAKER_01] Osobno, meni se sviđa ta forma.

348
00:22:50,079 --> 00:22:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Opuštena, zapravo sam i počeo to raditi.

349
00:22:52,640 --> 00:22:53,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ja se nadam da ćeš uspjeti.

350
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:56,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ja se nadam, ali što bude meni dobro.

351
00:22:57,279 --> 00:23:02,640
