416
00:26:39,519 --> 00:26:40,799
[SPEAKER_00] A što se na kraju desilo?

417
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:42,079
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je rezultat toga bio?

418
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek neki tragičan.

419
00:26:44,640 --> 00:26:45,440
[SPEAKER_00] Uvijek neko sranje.

420
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] Pa najbolje pa to potkad možemo.

421
00:26:48,880 --> 00:26:51,759
[SPEAKER_01] Jer velim došlo je do toga sjećate se olimpijade.

422
00:26:53,039 --> 00:26:56,400
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju je ispalo da je Fire, on je boksar, da je ipak muško.

423
00:26:57,519 --> 00:26:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] Evo sad imam zadnju vijest.

424
00:26:59,039 --> 00:27:00,640
[SPEAKER_00] Da nisam to, nisam to pratila.

425
00:27:00,640 --> 00:27:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam popratila, to je.

426
00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:02,240
[SPEAKER_01] Nispo ipak je muško.

427
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] A joj, jesam, če se sjećam.

428
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:07,519
[SPEAKER_01] Znači muško, ja se volim malo crni humor, malo volim biti ciničan.

429
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:09,599
[SPEAKER_01] Znači muško je matilo legalno žene tamo.

430
00:27:09,759 --> 00:27:10,960
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ali okej, to nije u redu.

431
00:27:11,200 --> 00:27:12,640
[SPEAKER_00] U tom slučaju, u tom slučaju.

432
00:27:12,799 --> 00:27:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ispalo je sada, evo, bar su tako u mediju objavili da ipak muškarac.

433
00:27:17,279 --> 00:27:17,759
[SPEAKER_01] I šta sad?

434
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:25,359
[SPEAKER_00] U tom slučaju to ne opravdavam zato jer su iskoristili tu svoju odluku i dobiti transrodna osoba u sportu.

435
00:27:26,000 --> 00:27:26,480
[SPEAKER_01] I šta sad?

436
00:27:27,039 --> 00:27:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš današnju vijest, zavaravaju se mi iz koje zemlje, odbačka reprezentacija, frajerija, prodose po ženu, smečira 130 km na sat je čim.

437
00:27:37,519 --> 00:27:39,119
[SPEAKER_01] Sude se bune nikom ništa.

438
00:27:40,960 --> 00:27:41,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kožiš?

439
00:27:41,680 --> 00:27:41,759
[UNKNOWN] Ne.

440
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:42,559
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono.

441
00:27:45,759 --> 00:27:47,680
[SPEAKER_01] Živa istina, počitajte malo novine.

442
00:27:47,839 --> 00:27:49,759
[SPEAKER_01] Franš se uvali u žensku ekipu.

443
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:51,279
[SPEAKER_01] Sad misliš šta je ono.

444
00:27:52,799 --> 00:27:53,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naravno.

445
00:27:54,160 --> 00:27:59,920
