456
00:28:21,359 --> 00:28:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] Da, sve je ono u medijima.

457
00:28:23,839 --> 00:28:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je to i to, kužniče.

458
00:28:27,440 --> 00:28:32,079
[SPEAKER_01] Influencerice, blogerice, ali ti si humanitarka velika, to smo zaboravili, dobila si i nagradu.

459
00:28:32,480 --> 00:28:33,359
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se nagrada zove?

460
00:28:34,000 --> 00:28:35,200
[SPEAKER_01] Ponos Hrvatske, točno da.

461
00:28:35,680 --> 00:28:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] Da, ne volim to isticati.

462
00:28:37,119 --> 00:28:37,839
[SPEAKER_01] Pa moramo te malo.

463
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:47,359
