465
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,240
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, gradila mi se sve poreze.

466
00:28:51,359 --> 00:28:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, sve je to humanitarno na kraju ispalo neka prevara.

467
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne sve, ali većina toga.

468
00:28:58,559 --> 00:28:58,640
[UNKNOWN] Da.

469
00:28:58,960 --> 00:29:03,279
