473
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:07,839
[SPEAKER_01] Da, ali velika većina.

474
00:29:08,160 --> 00:29:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moram reći svi, ali ispalo je u dosta slučajeva da na kraju za te koje sam pomagala, sam ih raskrinkavala.

475
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:18,799
[SPEAKER_00] Offakat.

476
00:29:19,839 --> 00:29:20,640
[SPEAKER_01] I to je stvarno.

477
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:23,359
[SPEAKER_01] To je bio game set meč kod tebe, evo pogledaš.

478
00:29:23,680 --> 00:29:24,880
